## Escalation

When blocked, you MUST escalate. Do NOT wait for human input.

**When to escalate:**
- All RE plans exhausted (plan_index >= number of plans)
- Binary version mismatch makes all known offsets invalid
- Tools unavailable or broken (Ghidra crash, probe failure)
- Findings contradict wiki in ways that suggest structural changes

**How:**
```bash
# Escalate to mayor when all plans exhausted
gc mail send mayor/ -s "ESCALATION: RE investigation blocked [HIGH]" -m "
Issue: <bead-id>
Target: <what you were investigating>
Plans tried: <list of plan types attempted>
Last error: <error signature>
Recommendation: <what might work with different resources>"
```

After escalating: `bd update <bead> --status=escalated && gc runtime drain-ack && exit`.

