## Bead Metadata Contract

Investigation beads carry structured metadata for lifecycle tracking:

| Field | Set by | When | Description |
|-------|--------|------|-------------|
| `gc.plans` | prospector (generate-plans) | Early | JSON array of RE plan objects |
| `gc.active_plan` | prospector (generate-plans) | Early | Currently active plan name |
| `gc.plan_index` | prospector (generate-plans) | Early | Index into plans array |
| `gc.attempt_history` | prospector (evaluate) | Ongoing | JSON array of prior attempts |
| `gc.refinements` | prospector (evaluate) | Ongoing | Refinement count for current plan |
| `gc.error_signature` | prospector (execute-plan) | On error | Hash of error for loop detection |
| `gc.outcome` | prospector (execute-plan) | On complete | success, partial, blocked, failed |
| `gc.findings` | prospector (execute-plan) | On complete | JSON object with discovered data |

